            ></path>
          </svg>
          WiFi validation/verification
        </p>

        <p class="mx-auto mb-2 flex items-center md:mx-0 lg:mb-0">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="2"
