            ></path>
          </svg>
          Site analysis and reporting
        </p>

        <p class="mx-auto mb-2 flex items-center md:mx-0 lg:mb-0">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke="currentColor"
            class="mr-2 h-5 w-5"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          Configuration and staging services
        </p>

        <p class="mx-auto mb-2 flex items-center md:mx-0 lg:mb-0">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke="currentColor"
            class="mr-2 h-5 w-5"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          Installation services
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Wirelesscarousel />
</MainLayout>
